node.title: Police release photo after Cleo Smith found alive locked in Carnarvon house
node.alt: A little girl sits in a hospital bed smiling
node.description: Police have posted a photo of a smiling Cleo Smith, pictured in hospital, hours after she was rescued from a house in the coastal West Australian town of Carnarvon.
node.content: ["Police have posted a photo of a smiling Cleo Smith, pictured in hospital, hours after she was rescued from a house in the coastal West Australian town of Carnarvon.", "The little girl is waving and holding an icy pole as she smiles at the camera.", "Cleo was found\u00a0alive in a locked house 18 days after she vanished from a family camping trip.", "More to come."]
